---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Dmytro Klevakin"
  description="Architect by day, automator by evening, live-coder by night. 12+ years in cloud, DevOps and architecture at SoftServe."
>
  <section class="page">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="div-label">About</div>
      <div class="about-grid">

        <!-- LEFT: portrait + facts -->
        <div>
          <div class="portrait">
            <div class="ph">
              PORTRAIT
              <b>Replace with your photo</b>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="facts">
            <span class="pill"><span class="dot"></span>Dnipro, Ukraine</span>
            <span class="pill">UA · RU · EN</span>
            <span class="pill">12+ yrs</span>
            <span class="pill">Azure / AWS / GCP</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT: bio + timeline + credentials -->
        <div>
          <h2>Architect by day, automator by evening, live-coder by night.</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top:18px">
            I started as a system administrator, grew into DevOps, then into cloud architecture.
            Today I lead Azure Solutions and the CoE — Critical Services at <strong>SoftServe</strong>,
            where I help teams design distributed, scalable and secure cloud-native systems.
          </p>
          <p class="lead">
            I think in systems — partly because I have a master's in theoretical physics, partly because
            I have a second master's in educational psychology, and partly because I trained as an NLP
            Master Practitioner and professional coach. Useful combo when an architecture problem turns
            out to be a people problem.
          </p>

          <div class="div-label" style="margin-top:36px">Experience</div>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="tl-row">
              <div class="y">2023 — now</div>
              <div class="b">
                <strong>Azure Solutions Lead · SoftServe</strong>
                <span>CI/CD &amp; cloud assessments, pre-sales, Microsoft Advanced Specializations, R&amp;D for Azure / Azure DevOps.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-row">
              <div class="y">2019 — 2023</div>
              <div class="b">
                <strong>DevOps Architect · SoftServe</strong>
                <span>DevOps knowledge model, operational support, leading the company-wide interviewers' community.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-row">
              <div class="y">2018 — 2019</div>
              <div class="b">
                <strong>IT Academy Expert · SoftServe</strong>
                <span>Built a DevOps course from scratch and mentored students.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-row">
              <div class="y">2016 — 2019</div>
              <div class="b">
                <strong>Lead DevOps Engineer · SoftServe</strong>
                <span>Managed teams up to 20 people, owned CI/CD and cloud-migration support.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-row">
              <div class="y">2012 — 2016</div>
              <div class="b">
                <strong>DevOps Engineer · SoftServe / FEEDGEE / Sitecore</strong>
                <span>Deployment, CI services, release management, application monitoring.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-row">
              <div class="y">2009 — 2012</div>
              <div class="b">
                <strong>System / network admin · Volia, TRC Falstap</strong>
                <span>Linux/FreeBSD, Cisco, Hyper-V, monitoring stacks.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="div-label" style="margin-top:36px">Credentials</div>
          <div class="cred">
            <div class="c"><div class="l">Certification</div><b>AZ-400 — Microsoft DevOps Solutions</b></div>
            <div class="c"><div class="l">Coaching</div><b>NLP Master Practitioner · Professional Coach · Business Trainer</b></div>
            <div class="c"><div class="l">Education</div><b>M.Phys, Theoretical Physics — Dnipropetrovsk National University</b></div>
            <div class="c"><div class="l">Education</div><b>M.Ed, Educational Psychology — Dnipropetrovsk National University</b></div>
            <div class="c"><div class="l">Publication</div><b>Designing eLearning course using LMS MOODLE</b></div>
            <div class="c"><div class="l">Languages</div><b>Ukrainian · Russian (native) · English (working)</b></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.4fr; gap: 48px; align-items: start; }
  @media (max-width: 780px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; } }

  .portrait {
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 340px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .portrait::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 14px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
  }
  .portrait::after {
    content: 'DK';
    position: absolute;
    right: -18px;
    bottom: -46px;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 240px;
    color: var(--navy-soft);
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    line-height: 1;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .portrait .ph {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .portrait .ph b {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }

  .facts { margin-top: 18px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
  .facts .pill { font-size: 12px; padding: 6px 12px; }

  .timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-top: 8px; }
  .tl-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: 18px; padding: 18px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); align-items: start; }
  .tl-row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .tl-row .y { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
  .tl-row .b { font-size: 15px; }
  .tl-row .b strong { display: block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2px; font-size: 15.5px; }
  .tl-row .b span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }

  .cred { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 8px; margin-top: 14px; }
  .cred .c { padding: 14px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--r-md); font-size: 13.5px; }
  .cred .c .l { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .cred .c b { font-weight: 600; }
</style>
